            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nomine <expan><abbr>Camulorigi</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> et Titocun<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> molam quam perdederunt <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>in fanum <note>sic</note> dei devovi cuicumque num<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>n <note>sic</note> involasit <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mola</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> illam ut <expan><abbr>sanguin</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> suum mittat usque diem quo <lb n="4"/>moriatur q<supplied reason="lost">ui</supplied>cumque invo<supplied reason="lost">l</supplied>a<supplied reason="lost">sit!</supplied> furta moriatur <lb n="5"/>et PAVLATORIAM quicumque <supplied reason="lost">illam</supplied> involasit <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>et ipse mo<supplied reason="lost">ri</supplied>atur <expan><abbr>quicumqu</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> illam <lb n="7"/>involasit <note>sic</note> et VERTOGN de hospitio vel vissacio <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>quicumque illam involasit <note>sic</note> a devo <note>sic</note> mori<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>tur</abbr></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bleitafel. Schriftrichtung rechts nach links. Buchstaben spiegelverkehrt. Gebet für Gerechtigkeit.</p>
            </div>
